section.para:
An instance is defined by a JSON file inside the instances
                sub-folder in one of the configuration locations. The name of the file also defines
                the instance name. Thus the file instances/falko.json defines
                the instance named
                "falko".{
 "display-name": "Falko",
 "default-querybuilder": "tigersearch",
 "default-corpusset": "falko-essays",
 "corpus-sets": [
  {
    "name": "falko-essays", 
    "corpus": ["falko-essay-l1", "falko-essay-l2"]
  },
  {
    "name": "falko-summaries", 
    "corpus": ["falko-summary-l1", "falko-summary-l2"]
  }
 ]
}
